name: The Chic Daily Tote in Turq Ombre
description:
The Chic Daily Tote handbag is a great bag for your everyday busy lifestyle. It's big enough to hold all of your belongings and it has an inside pocket with separate compartments for your keys, your sunglasses and your phone. The straps are made of genuine leather and will fit comfortably over your shoulder.

Note: This bag is dyed by hand - which is what makes it special. The dye pattern will vary slightly, but the overall look will be as you see it here.

name: Puffer Tote in Natural
description: The Puffer Tote bag is made of durable natural color quilted canvas, lined with indigo chambray and trimmed with orange nylon canvas and genuine leather handles. There is a pocket on the interior with separate compartments for your keys, your phone and your sunglasses. The interior is roomy enough to hold lots of stuff!

name: The Chic Social Tote in Indigo Ombre
description:
The Chic Social Tote is a fashionable, everyday handbag. It is just the right size to hold all of your daily needs, and then some. The bag is made of canvas and is fully lined with canvas. The outer pocket is made of genuine fur hide. There is also an interior pocket with separate compartments for your keys, your phone and your sunglasses. The handles are the perfect length to fit comfortably over your shoulder for wearing around town.

Note: the fur hide color and pattern will vary for each style. If you would like to know what we have in stock, please contact us when ordering.

name: The Chic Social Tote in Denim & Canvas
description:
The Chic Social Tote is a fashionable, everyday handbag. It is just the right size to hold all of your daily needs, and then some. The bag is made of indigo denim and is fully lined with natural canvas. The outer pocket is made of genuine fur hide. There is also an interior denim pocket with separate compartments for your keys, your phone and your sunglasses. The genuine leather handles are the perfect length to fit comfortably over your shoulder for wearing around town.

Note: the fur hide color and pattern will vary for each style. Some will be only brown (which looks great, too!). If you would like to know what we have in stock, please contact us ahead of ordering your bag.
